               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350615-name-196" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18350615-name-196" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350615-name-196" type="surname" value="LOVEGROVE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350615-name-196" type="given" value="THOMAS PARKER"></interp>THOMAS PARKER LOVEGROVE</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Shoreditch, and am a licensed victualler. I was coming out of my house on the 8th of June, and stopped the prisoner in my passage, with a parcel under his right arm—I said, "You scoundrel, why do you come running through my house in this manner?"—I turned him round, and this parcel dropped from him—I seized him by the collar, stooped and picked the cloth up—he said, "I will go back"—I said, "You shall not go back, you shall go with me"—my next door neighbour's shopman told me to take him to Mr. Rotherham—I took him there, and the cloth—Mr. Rotherham identified it—the prisoner said nothing.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi>, He says I had the parcel under my arm? <hi rend="italic">Witness</hi>. Yes; there was no other person in the passage between you and me—I swear I saw it under your arm—I saw it drop—I was on the passage side—no person came up to you and then ran away.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350615-name-197" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18350615-name-197" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350615-name-197" type="surname" value="ROTHERHAM"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350615-name-197" type="given" value="JEREMIAH"></interp>JEREMIAH ROTHERHAM</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a linen-draper, and live three or four doors from the last witness. This linen was brought to me by him and the prisoner—I can swear it is mine—I missed such a piece—I saw it safe half an hour before.</p>
