               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>, I went through this person's house—the door was pushed against me—a person with a blue coat ran violently past me—the witness took me into his house—he then took me out again—he saw this cloth, and said, "You have dropped this"—I said, "No; I beg your par<lb></lb>don, I never saw it before. "</p>
